SQLView.name: FS_FSDATA_PROJECTS
SQLView.sql: SELECT id, '<' || expt.project || '>' || xs_a_concat(', ' || shared.project) AS projects FROM xnat_experimentData expt LEFT JOIN xnat_experimentData_share shared ON expt.id=shared.sharing_share_xnat_experimentda_id LEFT JOIN xdat_meta_element xme ON expt.extension = xme.xdat_meta_element_id WHERE element_name='fs:fsData' GROUP BY expt.id,expt.project
